channel.title: Comments on: Dinosaur Jr. “Been There All the Time” on Late Night with Conan O’Brien 09.06.2007

item.title: By: patrick
item.dc:creator: patrick
item.description: agreed: the new dino record is pretty sweet. it's no <i>you're living all over me</i>, but it's still better than ninety-nine percent of anything else released this year.
